author: Microsoft
description:
Swiggy is one of India’s leading on-demand convenience platforms. Powered by Microsoft Fabric Real-Time Intelligence, Swiggy unifies data from traffic signals, rider locations, and thousands of dark stores to analyze millions of orders in near real time, improving demand prediction, inventory management, and order delivery. 

With data latency cut from minutes to seconds and analytics that now run in minutes instead of hours, customers get accurate ETAs they can plan their day around. Read about how Real-Time Intelligence enables Swiggy to deliver orders in 10 minutes: https://aka.ms/AAy4e44
